snippet.title: All You Can Eat - Greenlight Video
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/663240

Try a game unlike anything you've tried before!

All You can Eat - after ten years of living in a diner with a single "All You Can Eat" coupon, your existence is threatened by the diners imminent foreclosure! Embark on a epic mundane journey to protect your way of life!

 * The first interactive comic in the history of gaming!!! (that we know of!)
 * Impressive 20 minutes of gameplay! (at best!)
 * NO multiple endings, guaranteed!

Feed your inner freeloader!
